   :widths: 25 20 60
   :header-rows: 1

   * - Status Code Group
     - Commonly Used
     - Description
   * - 2XX
     - 200, 201, 204
     - Request was successful 
   * - 3XX
     - True
     - resource exists but representation cannot be sent back to requester
   * - 4XX
     - False
     - user not authorized to access resource
   * - 5XX
     - False
     - resource at PATH does not exist

